---
// Newsletter Component
---
<section class="newsletter">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="newsletter-card glass-card">
      <div class="newsletter-content">
        <h2>¡Únete a nuestra manada! 🐾</h2>
        <p>Suscríbete a nuestro boletín y recibe un <strong>15% de descuento</strong> en tu primera compra, además de tips exclusivos para tu mascota.</p>
        
        <form class="newsletter-form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();">
          <div class="input-group">
            <input type="email" placeholder="Tu correo electrónico" required aria-label="Correo electrónico" />
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Suscribirme</button>
          </div>
          <p class="form-hint">Prometemos no enviar spam, solo amor peludo.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div class="newsletter-image">
        <!-- Generando un perro y gato asomándose usando una imagen placeholder de alta calidad o CSS -->
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1543852786-1cf6624b9987?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" alt="Mascotas felices" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .newsletter {
    padding: 2rem 0 6rem;
  }
  
  .newsletter-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-light) 0%, var(--color-primary) 100%);
    border: none;
    overflow: hidden;
    color: var(--color-white);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .newsletter-content {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 60px;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  
  .newsletter-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  
  .newsletter-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
    max-width: 500px;
  }
  
  .newsletter-form {
    max-width: 450px;
  }
  
  .input-group {
    display: flex;
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: 6px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-sm);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  
  .input-group input {
    flex: 1;
    border: none;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    outline: none;
    background: transparent;
  }
  
  .input-group .btn {
    padding: 12px 24px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    border-radius: calc(var(--border-radius-sm) - 4px);
  }
  
  .form-hint {
    margin-top: 12px !important;
    font-size: 0.85rem !important;
    opacity: 0.8 !important;
  }
  
  .newsletter-image {
    flex: 1;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 400px;
    position: relative;
    clip-path: polygon(15% 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);
  }
  
  .newsletter-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .newsletter-card {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    
    .newsletter-content {
      padding: 40px 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .newsletter-content p {
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    }
    
    .newsletter-form {
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .newsletter-image {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 300px;
      clip-path: none;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .input-group {
      flex-direction: column;
      background: transparent;
      box-shadow: none;
      padding: 0;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    
    .input-group input {
      background: var(--color-white);
      border-radius: var(--border-radius-sm);
    }
    
    .input-group .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
